<div class="lead-in">
            <p class="lead-in__title" id="do-you-have-experience-in-or-with-the-plastics-industry-tell-us-about-it">Do You Have Experience in or With the Plastics Industry? Tell Us About It.</p>
                <div class="lead-in__intro">
            <p>Help journalists at the investigative nonprofit newsroom ProPublica examine plastics from creation to recycling and disposal. If you’ve worked in or been affected by the plastics industry, we want to hear from you.</p>

        </div>
    </div>


        <div class="bb-callout__wrapper">
            <script type="text/javascript" src="https://propublica.jotform.com/jsform/232602691519861"></script>
